DOC.brief_summary: The aim of this study was to investigate circulating concentrations of vaspin in fetal and neonatal samples from SGA, AGA and LGA with the respective insulin concentrations. Serum vaspin concentrations were determined by enzyme immunoassay in 22 SGA and 30 LGA and 30 AGA singleton full-term fetuses and neonates on cord blood and postnatal day 5.
DOC.brief_title: Vaspin Levels Compared With Serum Insulin and Blood Glucose Levels in Neonates
DOC.criteria: Full term healthy infant sepsis congenital anomaly sick infant
